{"id":552,"ayahs":[{"number":6,"arabic":"وَإِذْ قَالَ عِيسَى ٱبْنُ مَرْيَمَ يَٰبَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ إِنِّى رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ إِلَيْكُم مُّصَدِّقًۭا لِّمَا بَيْنَ يَدَىَّ مِنَ ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ وَمُبَشِّرًۢا بِرَسُولٍۢ يَأْتِى مِنۢ بَعْدِى ٱسْمُهُۥٓ أَحْمَدُ ۖ فَلَمَّا جَآءَهُم بِٱلْبَيِّنَٰتِ قَالُوا۟ هَٰذَا سِحْرٌۭ مُّبِينٌۭ","translation":"And [this happened, too,] when Jesus, the son of Mary, said: \"O children of Israel! Behold, I am an apostle of God unto you, [sent] to confirm the truth of whatever there still remains of the Torah, and to give [you] the glad tiding of an apostle who shall come after me, whose name shall be Ahmad.\" But when he [whose coming Jesus had foretold] came unto them with all evidence of the truth, they said: \"This [alleged message of his] is [nothing but] spellbinding eloquence!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5169.mp3","surahId":61,"words":[{"id":6295,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6296,"position":2,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6297,"position":3,"arabic":"عِيسَى","translation":"ঈসা","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6298,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱبْنُ","translation":"পুত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6299,"position":5,"arabic":"مَرْيَمَ","translation":"মারয়ামের","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6300,"position":6,"arabic":"يَـٰبَنِىٓ","translation":"\"হে বনী","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6301,"position":7,"arabic":"إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ","translation":"\"ইসরাইল","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6302,"position":8,"arabic":"إِنِّى","translation":"আমি নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6303,"position":9,"arabic":"رَسُولُ","translation":"রাসূূল","audioUrl":"wbw/061_006_009.mp3","